    "However, if using general access LLMs, this uncertainty could be reduced by ensuring that LLM parameters are set to reduce the level of randomness in responses by asking the LLM to repeat all tasks and then identifying (and discarding) outliers in the responses and by using a specific version of an LLM, e.g.",
